<div class="swnr-mta-active-mage-sight-chat swnr-mage-chat-roll-wrap">
  <div class="dice-roll">
    <div  class="swnr-mage-chat-roll-content">
      <h2>{{actor.name}} attempts a revelation.</h2>
        <table>
          <tbody>
            <tr><th>Arcanum</th><td>{{arcanum.name}}</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div class="dice-result">
      <h4 class="swnr-mage-chat-roll-section-title">Revelation Roll</h4>
      <div class="dice-tooltip" style="display: none;">
        <div class="dice-formula swnr-mage-chat-roll-dice-formula">{{r.formula}}</div>
        <section class="tooltip-part">
          <div class="dice">
            <ol class="dice-rolls">
              {{#each r.dice as |dice|}}
                {{#each dice.results as |roll|}}
                  <li class="roll die d10
                  {{#if roll.success}}success{{/if}}
                  {{#if roll.exploded}}exploded{{/if}}
                  ">{{roll.result}}</li>
                {{/each}}
              {{/each}}
            </ol>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
      <h4 class="dice-total swnr-mage-chat-roll-total-successes swnr-mage-chat-roll-result-{{successType}}">
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'exceptional'}}
          Exceptional Success
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'success'}}
          Success
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'failure'}}
          Failure
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'dramafail'}}
          Dramatic Failure
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        <small>Successes: {{r.result}}</small>
      </h4>

        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'exceptional'}}
          <p>The mage discovers the surface information of the Myster and can either lower the Myster's Opacity rating by 1, or, at the Storyteller's discretion, uncover one piece of deep information.</p>
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'success'}}
          <p>The mage discovers the surface information (p. 94) of the Mystery.</p>
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'failure'}}
          <p>The mage is unable to Reveal anything about the subject. She can still attempt to Scrutinize it however.</p>
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
        {{#swnr-space-magic-if-equals successType 'dramafail'}}
          <p>The mage overloads her own perceptions and the subject of her study with Mana, akin to spilling a bottle of ink on a page she was deciphering. No Scrutiny or Revelation of that subject is possible - by <em>any</em> mage - for the next 24 hours. The Prime spell "Cleanse Pattern" can dissolve the Mana before then, allowing further Scrutiny.</em></p>
        {{/swnr-space-magic-if-equals}}
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="swnr-mta-collapse-wrap">
    <h4 class="swnr-mta-collapse-title">General Info
      <span>Expand</span>
    </h4>
    <div class="swnr-mta-collapse-content">
      <p>Revelation is an instant action. It can be undertaken when a mage first encounters a Mystery, revealing only the surface information (see p. 94), and also when a mage has unraveled some or all of the Mysteryâ€™s Opacity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
